rows.label: tlk45200153_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Alba Margen is the biggest city
in the whole Empire.

rows.label: tlk45200153_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Watching from here, you see all sorts
of people and goods coming in and
going out of the city.

rows.label: tlk45200153_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I guess nobody can tell if there are bad
people in among the crowd. Like the
ones who caused a ruckus not long ago.

rows.label: tlk45200153_02_msg0004
rows.name:
If only all bad people were as easy to
spot as that Brionac lot.

rows.label: tlk45200153_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Oh, Brionac's an evil organization that
Emperor Nefer's trying to defeat.
